  "_note": "Maven Reels typography system. Editable. The assembler resolves font_family to the first installed face, falling back to a clean system sans (Segoe UI Semibold on Windows). No thick black outline anywhere — hierarchy comes from weight, size, soft shadow and a translucent backplate.",
